the entrepreneur ( italian : l'industriale ) is a 2011 italian drama film directed by giuliano montaldo . the film premiered out of competition at the 2011 rome film festival . it won three italian golden globes for best film , cinematography and best music and the special jury prize to pierfrancesco favino . it was also nominated to four nastro d'argento awards ( for best script , best actress , best cinematography and best scenography ) .